  "keyFeatures": [
    "Test executor for running WASI tests against any WebAssembly runtime",
    "Support for WASI preview 1 and preview 3",
    "Runtime adapter system supporting wasmtime, wasmedge, wamr, wazero, pywasm, and wizard",
    "Tests written in C, Rust, and AssemblyScript",
    "Operation-based JSON test specification format",
    "Precompiled test binaries for easy onboarding",
    "Daily test results branch for tracking runtime compliance",
    "Support for network proposals (HTTP, sockets)"
